            <html:p>
A <html:strong>Borel measure</html:strong> on a <fr:link href="/gtop-0002/" title="Topological Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0002/" display-uri="gtop-0002" type="local">topological space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is a measure <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mu  : \mathcal {B}(X) \to  [0, \infty ]]]></fr:tex> defined on the <fr:link href="/gtop-000K/" title="Borel \sigma -algebra" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000K/" display-uri="gtop-000K" type="local">Borel <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\sigma ]]></fr:tex>-algebra</fr:link>.
