            <fr:title text="Borel Set">Borel Set</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
A <html:strong>Borel set</html:strong> in a <fr:link href="/gtop-0002/" title="Topological Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0002/" display-uri="gtop-0002" type="local">topological space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is any set belonging to the <fr:link href="/gtop-000K/" title="Borel \sigma -algebra" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000K/" display-uri="gtop-000K" type="local">Borel <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\sigma ]]></fr:tex>-algebra</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {B}(X)]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
